---
import { getCollection } from "astro:content";
import ArticleList from "../components/ArticleList.astro";
import ProjectList from "../components/ProjectList.astro";
import { projects } from "../data/projects";
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
const recentNotes = (await getCollection("blog")).sort((a, b) => b.data.pubDate.valueOf() - a.data.pubDate.valueOf()).slice(0, 3);
---
<BaseLayout><section class="hero"><p class="eyebrow">你好，我是邓权耀</p><h1>记录 AI 学习<br />与项目实践。</h1><p class="lead">我是一名电子信息软件方向的研究生。这里放学习笔记、源码阅读和项目记录，尽量把正在理解的问题写清楚。</p></section><section class="section now-section"><div class="section-label">最近在做</div><div class="now-copy"><p>正在学习 Agent 系统的工程化实现，也在用 Docker、PostgreSQL 和 FastAPI 搭一个能持续迭代的小实验环境。</p><a class="text-link" href="/blog">查看学习笔记 →</a></div></section><section class="section"><div class="section-heading"><div class="section-label">项目记录</div><a class="text-link" href="/projects">全部项目 →</a></div><ProjectList items={projects.slice(0, 3)} /></section><section class="section"><div class="section-heading"><div class="section-label">最新笔记</div><a class="text-link" href="/blog">全部笔记 →</a></div><ArticleList entries={recentNotes} /></section></BaseLayout>
